{"tid":2186414,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新宿重演8.31 手足：續揭港共惡行","createTime":"2020-09-03T03:03:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T04:50:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0a47caa50b2cdec4fece7a423734ea29843de27f","tid":2186414,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T03:03:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200903/XIDQKN3KRVHBHKVXDXWHELIRHU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200903%2FXIDQKN3KRVHBHKVXDXWHELIRHU%2F&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hfGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=5b029de6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200903%2FXIDQKN3KRVHBHKVXDXWHELIRHU%2F&h=3a4116a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200903/XIDQKN3KRVHBHKVXDXWHELIRHU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n新宿重演8.31 手足：續揭港共惡行<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eETs05CMpm7ZRHBY2iDW5xaiH0A=/1259x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QDDYCP53NFAQVOP4EHEPTMAA64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeETs05CMpm7ZRHBY2iDW5xaiH0A%3D%2F1259x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQDDYCP53NFAQVOP4EHEPTMAA64.jpg&h=410416a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■日本手足在新宿站外重演港鐵乘客面對警員施襲時跪地求饒的場面。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】日前是太子站8.31事件一周年，大批港人拒絕遺忘，在站。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n播放遇襲市民慘叫聲<br />\n<br />\nfacebook專頁「Stand with Hong Kong at JPN」昨日上載多幅相片及影片，並貼文指「8.31一周年，一班手足在東京。。。。。。。。。。。FreeAgnes」、「#freejimmylai」及「#StandWithHongKong」等。<br />\n<br />\n從該fb專頁上載的片段可見，多人在新宿站南口一段行人路外，重演多幕速龍小隊警員在太子站無差別打市民的情況，包括一男一女在車廂內被警員打時跪地求饒、警員捉住黑衣人要求他跪地面壁，以及義務急救員在太子站外要求入內救援但被警員拒絕。片段中更播放了市民的慘叫聲、救護員哀求聲及港鐵車廂內的廣播聲。帖文至昨日有逾2,000人讚好，不少網民留言稱「多謝日本手足」，並感謝日本人與港人同行。"},{"pid":"f6b08a1065ed91827c6167c4d3e9809a4390c595","tid":2186414,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T03:05:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b68f96a14c6c6f8ea1070aeffbc24645894a616","tid":2186414,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T04:40:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80b91692b3e9819067c1d9c7bcad4c30ddb524e5","tid":2186414,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T04:46:03.000Z","msg":"新宿警署沒有主動拘捕及引渡這些人<br />\n<br />\n新宿警察局長等於支持他們用謊言意圖分裂中國的行為<br />\n已經違反港區國安法，嚴重干涉中國內政<br />\n希望新宿警察局長來港自首伏法，還法治一個公道"},{"pid":"608b24d13d7575ff9924d565bb1ed0110ba6f9ce","tid":2186414,"uid":291465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T04:48:23.000Z","msg":"第一張相嘅情景<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"488fb6e9a88b96694d0d1f9dbfd3af57826d2f26","tid":2186414,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T04:50:56.000Z","msg":"聯署支持封殺微信同TikTok<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fwe-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hfGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=74e2489a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok</a>"}]}